overview: August 10th, 2008 :: Kaiju's big bad, Dr. Cube, teams with The Order of the Neo Solar Temple against Mike Quackenbush and the Sea Donsters, while Incoherence and Claudio Castagnoli face off with the Osirian Portal and Brodie Lee! Matches featured:  1. Los Ice Creams vs Las Chivas  2. Chuck Taylor vs Fire Ant  3. The Fabulous Two vs Sara Del Rey & Bobby Dempsey  4. Jimmy Olsen vs Worker Ant  5. F.I.S.T. vs Super Smash Brothers  6. Young Lions Cup Match Vin Gerard vs Drake Younger  7. Dr. Cube, Crossbones & UltraMantis Black vs Mike Quackenbush & The SeaDonsters  8. Eddie Kingston vs Lince Dorado  9. Brodie Lee & Osirian Portal vs Incoherence & Claudio Castagnoli
title: Chikara Vanity And Violence
